Interface ISMap<VALUE>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,VALUE>

    public interface ISMap<VALUE>
extends java.util.Map<java.lang.String,VALUE>
    ISMap is an immutable map with keys that are strings, but with the addition of subMap and sortedKeySet methods.
